## Git Integration

### File-Level

```sh
cat file.{{ ext }}@/git/LOG.md              # commit log
cat file.{{ ext }}@/git/LOG.md:-10          # last 10 commits
cat file.{{ ext }}@/git/BLAME.md            # per-line authorship
cat file.{{ ext }}@/git/BLAME.md:42-55      # blame for line range
cat file.{{ ext }}@/git/CONTRIBUTORS.md     # contributors ranked
cat file.{{ ext }}@/diff/HEAD.diff          # uncommitted changes
cat file.{{ ext }}@/diff/main.diff          # diff against any branch
```

### Symbol-Level (Scoped to Symbol's Line Range)

```sh
cat file.{{ ext }}@/symbols/Foo@/git/LOG.md     # commits touching this symbol only
cat file.{{ ext }}@/symbols/Foo@/git/BLAME.md   # blame within the symbol
```

### Repository-Level

```sh
cat @/git/STATUS.md              # working tree status
ls @/git/branches/               # branch listing
mv @/git/branches/old @/git/branches/new   # rename a branch
```

### Cross-Branch Comparison

```sh
diff <(cat @/git/branches/main/src/lib.{{ ext }}@/symbols/process@/body.{{ ext }}) \
     <(cat @/git/branches/feature/src/lib.{{ ext }}@/symbols/process@/body.{{ ext }})
```

