## Markdown Documents

Markdown files decompose at headers into navigable sections:

```sh
cat doc.md@/symbols/OVERVIEW.md                    # section listing
cat doc.md@/symbols/20-getting-started.md          # read one section
cat doc.md@/symbols/20-getting-started/code/10.{{ ext }}   # extracted code block
```

Code blocks are extracted as editable files with extensions from the fence language tag.

